sentence: what are the flights on mondays that travel from charlotte north carolina to phoenix arizona
sq2:
SELECT DISTINCT  '"'||v0.flight_id||'"', '"'||v1.airport_code||'"',
 '"'||v2.city_code||'"', '"'||v2.city_name||'"', '"'||v3.state_code||'"',
 '"'||v3.state_name||'"', '"'||v4.airport_code||'"',
 '"'||v5.city_code||'"', '"'||v5.city_name||'"',
 '"'||v6.state_code||'"', '"'||v6.state_name||'"', '"'||v7.days_code||'"',
 '"'||v7.day_name||'"' FROM flight v0, airport_service v1,
 city v2, state v3, airport_service v4, city v5,
 state v6, days v7 
WHERE (((v0.from_airport = ANY v1.airport_code) 
AND ((v1.city_code = ANY v2.city_code) AND ((v2.city_name = 'CHARLOTTE') 
AND ((v2.state_code = ANY v3.state_code) 
AND (v3.state_name = 'NORTH CAROLINA'))))) AND (((v0.to_airport = ANY v4.airport_code) 
AND ((v4.city_code = ANY v5.city_code) 
AND ((v5.city_name = 'PHOENIX') AND ((v5.state_code = ANY v6.state_code) 
AND (v6.state_name = 'ARIZONA'))))) AND ((v0.flight_days = ANY v7.days_code) 
AND (v7.day_name = 'MONDAY'))));
sql: ( SELECT DISTINCT FLIGHT.FLIGHT_ID FROM FLIGHT WHERE ( FLIGHT . FROM_AIRPORT IN ( SELECT AIRPORT_SERVICE . AIRPORT_CODE FROM AIRPORT_SERVICE WHERE AIRPORT_SERVICE . CITY_CODE IN ( SELECT CITY . CITY_CODE FROM CITY WHERE ( CITY.CITY_NAME = ' CHARLOTTE ' AND CITY . STATE_CODE IN ( SELECT STATE . STATE_CODE FROM STATE WHERE STATE.STATE_NAME = ' NORTH CAROLINA ' ) ) ) ) AND ( FLIGHT . TO_AIRPORT IN ( SELECT AIRPORT_SERVICE . AIRPORT_CODE FROM AIRPORT_SERVICE WHERE AIRPORT_SERVICE . CITY_CODE IN ( SELECT CITY . CITY_CODE FROM CITY WHERE ( CITY.CITY_NAME = ' PHOENIX ' AND CITY . STATE_CODE IN ( SELECT STATE . STATE_CODE FROM STATE WHERE STATE.STATE_NAME = ' ARIZONA ' ) ) ) ) AND FLIGHT . FLIGHT_DAYS IN ( SELECT DAYS . DAYS_CODE FROM DAYS WHERE DAYS.DAY_NAME = ' MONDAY ' ) ) ) ) ;
